Feature: Subtract

Scenario: Subtract two numbers positive result
    Given I enter "10" into the calculator
    And I hit "subtract"
    And I enter "5" into the calculator
    When I hit "equals"
    Then I see a result of "5"

Scenario: Subtract three numbers positive result
    Given I enter "10" into the calculator
    And I hit "Subtract"
    And I enter "5" into the calculator
    And I hit "Subtract"
    And I enter "2" into the calculator
    When I hit "equals"
    Then I see a result of "3"

Scenario: Subtract two numbers negative result
    Given I enter "5" into the calculator
    And I hit "Subtract"
    And I enter "6" into the calculator
    When I hit "equals"
    Then I see a result of "-1"
	
Scenario: Subtract three numbers negative result
    Given I enter "5" into the calculator
    And I hit "Subtract"
    And I enter "5" into the calculator
    And I hit "Subtract"
    And I enter "2" into the calculator
    When I hit "equals"
    Then I see a result of "-2"
